@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gzgpzk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.97)) * ((v0 + 0.32 * v2 + 0.07) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.25)))
    tmp = 0.05
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.11 / v0 + 0.70)) + wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.35)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(v0) - wp.abs((v2 + 0.91 * tmp + 0.71)))
    data[tid] = v0
